Class AnnotationInstanceSupplier<T,E extends Annotation,F extends Annotation>

java.lang.Object
ru.introguzzle.parsers.common.mapping.deserialization.AnnotationInstanceSupplier<T,E,F>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the source object used during instance acquisition (e.g., XMLDocument)
E - the type of the entity-level annotation providing metadata for constructor argument mapping
F - the type of the field-level annotation
